title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (17): Adversarial Learning
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* (Generative) Adversarial Networks
* Where to use the Adversary?: Features vs. Outputs
* GANs on Discrete Outputs
* Adversaries on Features

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-17-adversarial.pdf

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/F1hZfoh-wX4
Next Video: https://youtu.be/EKvkrv4K0qo

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
